entries.journal_entry_description: Ziven Tissak will test your hunting abilities by asking you to hunt webweavers in Etyyy.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Go speak with Ziven Tissak at the primary Rodian hunting camp.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Ziven wants you to collect 38 untainted webweaver fangs. Any webweavers in the area could have them..
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: You have the webweaver fangs. Now return to Ziven at the main Rodian hunting camp.
